---
layout: base.liquid
---
{% render pageTitle, title: title %}
<div class="content">
  {{ content }}
</div>
<ul class="mb-10 grid list-none grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-5">
  {% for link in links %}
    <li class="mb-2">
      <a
        href="{{ link.url }}"
        target="_blank"
        class="block cursor-pointer border-4 border-solid border-transparent font-semibold text-yellow-300 hover:border-red-500 hover:bg-red-500 hover:text-stone-50"
      >
        {{- link.title -}}
      </a>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
{% render pageTitle, title: 'Webring' %}
<div class="content grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3">
  <div class="col-span-1">
    <p>
      This <a href="https://webring.xxiivv.com">webring</a> is an attempt to inspire artists &amp; developers to build
      their own website and share traffic among each other. The ring welcomes personalized websites such as diaries,
      wikis &amp; portfolios.
    </p>
    <p>
      To add yourself to the ring, submit a
      <a href="https://github.com/XXIIVV/webring#join-the-webring">pull request</a>.
    </p>
    <a href="https://webring.xxiivv.com/"><img src="https://webring.xxiivv.com/icon.white.svg"></a>
  </div>
</div>
